msgid "Intermediate Track"
msgstr ""

#: ../../scipy-conference/manual/committees/tutorials.rst:117
msgid ""
"Prerequisite should be basic understanding of SciPy stack, i.e. numpy, "
"scipy, matplotlib etc."
